'''Alan Peak''' ({{coord|72|39|S|0|11|E|}}) is a [[summit (topography)|peak]] at the west side of the mouth of [[Reece Valley]], in the south part of the [[Sverdrup Mountains]] in [[Queen Maud Land]].
